section 7_4

  |{Glossary.*Anthropogenic Anthropogenic} {Glossary.*Aerosol aerosol} is changing cloud properties, thus contributing a substantial {Topics.*Radiative_Forcing forcing} to the climate system. Since {cite.1.'IPCC_2007 AR4}, research has continued to articulate new pathways through which the aerosol may affect the radiative properties of clouds. The complexity of cloud system responses to aerosol perturbations has become more fully appreciated.


